metadata.name: dinosaur philosophy #1
metadata.description: 5 000 exclusive and never-before-seen comics by James Stewart (Author) and K Roméy (Illustrator). Posing questions such as ‘do I exist?’, ‘how should I live?’, ‘what is beauty?’ in each NFT comic, dinosaur characters explore how to exist in the modern world and meditate on what it means to ‘live well’. Secret physical drop to each minter. Official shop: https://shopdinosaur.com.
